Interface DicomDictionary

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDictionary, EmbbedDicomDictionary
public interface DicomDictionary

DICOM Dictionary.

a Dictionary Contains:

  • Tags
  • SopClasses
  • TransferSyntaxes
  • Modules
  • Macros
